snippet.title: MainFrames - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist MainFrames now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1521360/MainFrames/ 

We’re thrilled to announce that MainFrames is coming to you on March 6th! 
Get ready to embark on a cozy platforming adventure as an adorable little Floppy Disk searching for their purpose inside an operating system. 💾

Guide Floppy by rearranging program windows to create new pathways, and hop between frames to navigate the digital world.
